==Behind the scenes==
Mag-ball was first mentioned in [[A. C. Crispin]]'s [[1998]] novel ''[[Rebel Dawn]]'', the third entry of [[The Han Solo Trilogy (hardcover)|''The Han Solo Trilogy'']].<ref name="RD" /> The [[2011]] [[BioWare]] [[Star Wars video games|video game]] ''[[Star Wars: The Old Republic]]'' introduced an alternate spelling of the sport's name.<ref name="SWTOR" />

